{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I was listed on the online biography \n"},{"time":3000,"text":"that said I was a design missionary. \n"},{"time":6000,"text":"That's a bit lofty; I'm really more \n"},{"time":8000,"text":"of something like a street walker.\n"},{"time":10000,"text":"I spend a lot of time in urban areas \n"},{"time":12000,"text":"looking for design,"},{"time":14000,"text":"and studying design in the public sector. \n"},{"time":16000,"text":"I take about 5,000 photographs a year, \n"},{"time":19000,"text":"and I thought that I would edit from these,"},{"time":22000,"text":"and try to come up with some images \n"},{"time":25000,"text":"that might be appropriate and interesting to you."},{"time":27000,"text":"And I used three criteria:"},{"time":29000,"text":"the first was, I thought I'd talk about"},{"time":31000,"text":"real design within reach,"},{"time":33000,"text":"design that's free, not design not quite within reach,"},{"time":36000,"text":"as we're fondly known by our competition and competitors,"},{"time":39000,"text":"but stuff that you can find on the streets, stuff that was free,"},{"time":43000,"text":"stuff that was available to all people,"},{"time":45000,"text":"and stuff that probably contains some other important messages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":48000,"text":"I'll use these sidewalks in Rio as an example."},{"time":51000,"text":"A very common public design done in the '50s."},{"time":54000,"text":"It's got a nice kind of flowing, organic form,"},{"time":57000,"text":"very consistent with the Brazilian culture --"},{"time":60000,"text":"I think good design adds to culture."},{"time":62000,"text":"Wholly inconsistent with San Francisco or New York."},{"time":65000,"text":"But I think these are my sort of information highways:"},{"time":68000,"text":"I live in much more of an analog world,"},{"time":70000,"text":"where pedestrian traffic and"},{"time":72000,"text":"interaction and diversity exchange,"},{"time":75000,"text":"and where I think the simple things under our feet"},{"time":77000,"text":"have a great amount of meaning to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80000,"text":"How did I get started in this business?"},{"time":82000,"text":"I was a ceramic designer for about 10 years,"},{"time":84000,"text":"and just loved utilitarian form --"},{"time":87000,"text":"simple things that we use every day,"},{"time":89000,"text":"little compositions of color and surface on form."},{"time":92000,"text":"This led me to starting a company called Design Within Reach,"},{"time":96000,"text":"a company dealing with simple forms,"},{"time":98000,"text":"making good designers available to us,"},{"time":100000,"text":"and also selling the personalities and character of the designers"},{"time":103000,"text":"as well, and it seems to have worked."},{"time":106000,"text":"A couple of years into the process,"},{"time":108000,"text":"I spent a lot of time in Europe traveling around, looking for design."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111000,"text":"And I had a bit of a wake-up call in Amsterdam:"},{"time":113000,"text":"I was there going into the design stores,"},{"time":115000,"text":"and mixing with our crowd of designers,"},{"time":117000,"text":"and I recognized that a whole lot of stuff"},{"time":119000,"text":"pretty much looked the same, and the effect of globalization"},{"time":121000,"text":"has had that in our community also."},{"time":123000,"text":"We know a lot about what's going on with design around the world,"},{"time":126000,"text":"and it's getting increasingly more difficult"},{"time":128000,"text":"to find design that reflects a unique culture."},{"time":131000,"text":"I was walking around on the streets of Amsterdam"},{"time":133000,"text":"and I recognized, you know, the big story"},{"time":135000,"text":"from Amsterdam isn't what's in the design stores,"},{"time":137000,"text":"it's what's out on the streets,"},{"time":139000,"text":"and maybe it's self-explanatory,"},{"time":141000,"text":"but a city that hasn't been taken over by modernism,"},{"time":144000,"text":"that's preserved its kind of architecture and character,"},{"time":147000,"text":"and where the bicycle plays an important part of the way"},{"time":150000,"text":"in which people get around and where pedestrian rights"},{"time":152000,"text":"are protected."},{"time":154000,"text":"And I write a newsletter that goes out every week,"},{"time":156000,"text":"and I wrote an article about this, and it got such enormous response"},{"time":159000,"text":"that I realized that design, that common design,"},{"time":161000,"text":"that's in the public area means a lot to people,"},{"time":164000,"text":"and establishes kind of a groundwork and a dialog."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166000,"text":"I then kind of thought about the other cities"},{"time":169000,"text":"in Europe where I spend a lot of time looking for design,"},{"time":172000,"text":"like Basel, where Vitra is located, or in northern Italy --"},{"time":176000,"text":"all cities where there are a whole lot of bicycles,"},{"time":178000,"text":"and where pedestrian areas -- and I came to the conclusion that perhaps"},{"time":182000,"text":"there was something about these important design centers"},{"time":185000,"text":"that dealt with bicycles and foot traffic,"},{"time":187000,"text":"and I'm sure the skeptic eye would say, no, the correlation there"},{"time":189000,"text":"is that there are universities and schools"},{"time":191000,"text":"where people can't afford cars,"},{"time":193000,"text":"but it did seem that in many of these areas"},{"time":195000,"text":"pedestrian traffic was protected."},{"time":199000,"text":"You wouldn't look at this and call this a designer bike:"},{"time":202000,"text":"a designer bike is made of titanium or molybdenum."},{"time":204000,"text":"But I began looking at design in a place like Amsterdam"},{"time":207000,"text":"and recognized, you know, the first job of design"},{"time":209000,"text":"is to serve a social purpose."},{"time":211000,"text":"And so I look at this bike as not being a designer bike,"},{"time":215000,"text":"but being a very good example of design."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"And since that time in Amsterdam, I spent an increasing amount of time"},{"time":221000,"text":"in the cities, looking at design"},{"time":223000,"text":"for common evidence of design"},{"time":225000,"text":"that really isn't under so much of a designer's signature."},{"time":228000,"text":"I was in Buenos Aires very recently,"},{"time":230000,"text":"and I went to see this bridge by Santiago Calatrava."},{"time":234000,"text":"He's a Spanish architect and designer."},{"time":237000,"text":"And the tourist brochures pointed me in the direction of this bridge --"},{"time":240000,"text":"I love bridges, metaphorically and symbolically and structurally --"},{"time":243000,"text":"and it was a bit of a disappointment,"},{"time":245000,"text":"because of the sludge from the river was encrusted on it; it really wasn't in use."},{"time":248000,"text":"And I recognized that oftentimes design,"},{"time":250000,"text":"when you're set up to see design,"},{"time":252000,"text":"it can be a bit of a letdown."}]},{"cues":[{"time":254000,"text":"But there were lots of other things going on in this area:"},{"time":257000,"text":"it was a kind of construction zone;"},{"time":259000,"text":"a lot of buildings were going up."},{"time":261000,"text":"And, approaching a building from a distance, you don't see too much;"},{"time":263000,"text":"you get a little closer, and you arrive at a nice little composition"},{"time":266000,"text":"that might remind you of a Mondrian or a Diebenkorn or something."},{"time":270000,"text":"But to me it was an example of"},{"time":272000,"text":"industrial materials with a little bit of colors and animation"},{"time":275000,"text":"and a nice little still life -- kind of unintended piece of design."},{"time":278000,"text":"And going a little closer, you get a different perspective."},{"time":281000,"text":"I find these little vignettes,"},{"time":283000,"text":"these little accidental pieces of design,"},{"time":285000,"text":"to be refreshing."},{"time":287000,"text":"They give me, I don't know,"},{"time":289000,"text":"a sense of correctness in the world"},{"time":291000,"text":"and some visual delight in the knowledge"},{"time":294000,"text":"that the building will probably never look as good"},{"time":296000,"text":"as this simple industrial scaffolding"},{"time":298000,"text":"that is there to serve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300000,"text":"Down the road, there was another building, a nice visual structure:"},{"time":303000,"text":"horizontal, vertical elements, little decorative lines"},{"time":306000,"text":"going across, these magenta squiggles,"},{"time":308000,"text":"the workmen being reduced to decorative elements,"},{"time":311000,"text":"just a nice, kind of, breakup"},{"time":313000,"text":"of the urban place."},{"time":315000,"text":"And, you know, that no longer exists."},{"time":317000,"text":"You've captured it for a moment, and finding this little still life's"},{"time":319000,"text":"like listening to little songs or something:"},{"time":321000,"text":"it gives me an enormous amount of pleasure."},{"time":324000,"text":"Antoine Predock designed"},{"time":326000,"text":"a wonderful ball stadium in San Diego"},{"time":328000,"text":"called Petco Park."},{"time":330000,"text":"A terrific use of local materials,"},{"time":332000,"text":"but inside you could find some interior compositions."},{"time":335000,"text":"Some people go to baseball stadiums to look at games;"},{"time":337000,"text":"I go and see design relationships."},{"time":339000,"text":"Just a wonderful kind of breakup of architecture,"},{"time":341000,"text":"and the way that the trees form vertical elements."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344000,"text":"Red is a color in the landscape"},{"time":346000,"text":"that is often on stop signs."},{"time":348000,"text":"It takes your attention; it has a great amount of emotion;"},{"time":350000,"text":"it stares back at you the way that a figure might."},{"time":353000,"text":"Just a piece of barrier tape construction stuff in Italy."},{"time":356000,"text":"Construction site in New York:"},{"time":358000,"text":"red having this kind of emotional power"},{"time":360000,"text":"that's almost an equivalent with the way in which --"},{"time":362000,"text":"cuteness of puppies and such."},{"time":364000,"text":"Side street in Italy."},{"time":366000,"text":"Red drew me into this little composition,"},{"time":368000,"text":"optimistic to me in the sense that maybe"},{"time":371000,"text":"the public service's mailbox,"},{"time":373000,"text":"door service, plumbing."},{"time":375000,"text":"It looks as if these different public services"},{"time":377000,"text":"work together to create some nice little compositions."},{"time":380000,"text":"In Italy, you know, almost everything, kind of, looks good."},{"time":382000,"text":"Simple menus put on a board,"},{"time":383000,"text":"achieving, kind of, the sort of balance."},{"time":385000,"text":"But I'm convinced that it's because"},{"time":387000,"text":"you're walking around the streets and seeing things."},{"time":389000,"text":"Red can be comical: it can draw your attention"},{"time":391000,"text":"to the poor little personality of the little fire hydrant"},{"time":394000,"text":"suffering from bad civic planning in Havana."},{"time":397000,"text":"Color can animate simple blocks,"},{"time":399000,"text":"simple materials:"},{"time":401000,"text":"walking in New York, I'll stop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403000,"text":"I don't always know why I take photographs of things."},{"time":406000,"text":"A nice visual composition of symmetry."},{"time":408000,"text":"Curves against sharp things."},{"time":410000,"text":"It's a comment on the way in which we deal with"},{"time":413000,"text":"public seating in the city of New York."},{"time":415000,"text":"I've come across some other just,"},{"time":417000,"text":"kind of, curious relationships"},{"time":419000,"text":"of bollards on the street that have different interpretations,"},{"time":422000,"text":"but -- these things amuse me."},{"time":425000,"text":"Sometimes a trash can -- this is just in the street in San Francisco --"},{"time":428000,"text":"a trash can that's been left there for 18 months"},{"time":431000,"text":"creates a nice 45-degree angle"},{"time":433000,"text":"against these other relationships,"},{"time":435000,"text":"and turns a common parking spot into a nice little piece of sculpture."},{"time":438000,"text":"So, there's this sort of silent hand of design at work"},{"time":441000,"text":"that I see in places that I go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":444000,"text":"Havana is a wonderful area."},{"time":446000,"text":"It's quite free of commercial clutter:"},{"time":448000,"text":"you don't see our logos and brands and names,"},{"time":450000,"text":"and therefore you're alert to things physically."},{"time":452000,"text":"And this is a great protection of a pedestrian zone,"},{"time":457000,"text":"and the repurposing of some colonial cannons to do that."},{"time":461000,"text":"And Cuba needs to be far more resourceful,"},{"time":464000,"text":"because of the blockades and things,"},{"time":465000,"text":"but a really wonderful playground."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467000,"text":"I've often wondered why Italy is really a leader in modern design."},{"time":471000,"text":"In our area, in furnishings,"},{"time":473000,"text":"they're sort of way at the top."},{"time":475000,"text":"The Dutch are good also, but the Italians are good."},{"time":477000,"text":"And I came across this little street in Venice,"},{"time":480000,"text":"where the communist headquarters"},{"time":482000,"text":"were sharing a wall with this Catholic shrine."},{"time":485000,"text":"And I realized that, you know, Italy is a place"},{"time":488000,"text":"where they can accept these different ideologies"},{"time":492000,"text":"and deal with diversity and not have the problem,"},{"time":495000,"text":"or they can choose to ignore them,"},{"time":497000,"text":"but these -- you don't have warring factions,"},{"time":500000,"text":"and I think that maybe the tolerance of the absurdity"},{"time":503000,"text":"which has made Italy so innovative \n"},{"time":506000,"text":"and so tolerant."},{"time":508000,"text":"The past and the present work quite well together in Italy also,"},{"time":512000,"text":"and I think that it's recognizable there,"},{"time":514000,"text":"and has an important effect on culture,"},{"time":516000,"text":"because their public spaces are protected,"},{"time":518000,"text":"their sidewalks are protected,"},{"time":520000,"text":"and you're actually able to confront these things"},{"time":522000,"text":"physically,"},{"time":524000,"text":"and I think this helps people get over"},{"time":525000,"text":"their fear of modernism and other such things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528000,"text":"A change might be a typical street corner in San Francisco."},{"time":531000,"text":"And I use this -- this is, sort of,"},{"time":533000,"text":"what I consider to be urban spam."},{"time":535000,"text":"I notice this stuff because I walk a lot,"},{"time":538000,"text":"but here, private industry is really kind of"},{"time":540000,"text":"making a mess of the public sector."},{"time":542000,"text":"And as I look at it, I sort of say, you know,"},{"time":543000,"text":"the publications that report on problems in the urban area"},{"time":546000,"text":"also contribute to it,"},{"time":548000,"text":"and it's just my call to say to all of us,"},{"time":550000,"text":"public policy won't change this at all;"},{"time":552000,"text":"private industry has to work to take things like this seriously."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555000,"text":"The extreme might be in Italy where, again,"},{"time":558000,"text":"there's kind of some type of control"},{"time":560000,"text":"over what's happening in the environment is very evident,"},{"time":563000,"text":"even in the way that they sell and distribute periodicals."},{"time":566000,"text":"I walk to work every day or ride my scooter,"},{"time":569000,"text":"and I come down and park in this little spot."},{"time":573000,"text":"And I came down one day,"},{"time":575000,"text":"and all the bikes were red."},{"time":577000,"text":"Now, this is not going to impress you guys who Photoshop, and can do stuff,\n"},{"time":580000,"text":"but this was an actual moment"},{"time":582000,"text":"when I got off my bike,"},{"time":584000,"text":"and I looked and I thought, it's as if"},{"time":586000,"text":"all of my biker brethren"},{"time":589000,"text":"had kind of gotten together and conspired"},{"time":591000,"text":"to make a little statement."},{"time":593000,"text":"And it reminded me that --"},{"time":595000,"text":"to keep in the present,"},{"time":597000,"text":"to look out for these kinds of things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":599000,"text":"It gave me possibilities for wonder --"},{"time":601000,"text":"if maybe it's a yellow day in San Francisco, and we could all agree,"},{"time":604000,"text":"and create some installations."},{"time":606000,"text":"But it also reminded me of the power"},{"time":608000,"text":"of pattern and repetition"},{"time":610000,"text":"to make an effect in our mind."},{"time":613000,"text":"And I don't know if there's a stronger kind of effect"},{"time":616000,"text":"than pattern and the way it unites"},{"time":618000,"text":"kind of disparate elements."},{"time":620000,"text":"I was at the art show in Miami in December,"},{"time":623000,"text":"and spent a couple of hours looking at fine art,"},{"time":625000,"text":"and amazed at the prices of art"},{"time":627000,"text":"and how expensive it is, but having a great time looking at it."},{"time":629000,"text":"And I came outside, and the valets for this car service"},{"time":634000,"text":"had created, you know, quite a nice little collage"},{"time":637000,"text":"of these car keys,"},{"time":639000,"text":"and my closest equivalent were a group of prayer tags"},{"time":643000,"text":"that I had seen in Tokyo."},{"time":645000,"text":"And I thought that if"},{"time":647000,"text":"pattern can unite these disparate elements,"},{"time":650000,"text":"it can do just about anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":652000,"text":"I don't have very many shots of people,"},{"time":654000,"text":"because they kind of \nget in the way of studying pure form."},{"time":657000,"text":"I was in a small restaurant in Spain,"},{"time":660000,"text":"having lunch --"},{"time":662000,"text":"one of those nice days where"},{"time":664000,"text":"you had the place kind of to yourself,"},{"time":666000,"text":"and you have a glass of wine, and enjoying the local area"},{"time":668000,"text":"and the culture and the food"},{"time":670000,"text":"and the quiet, and feeling very lucky,"},{"time":673000,"text":"and a bus load of tourists arrived,"},{"time":676000,"text":"emptied out,"},{"time":678000,"text":"filled up the restaurant."},{"time":680000,"text":"In a very short period of time,"},{"time":682000,"text":"completely changed the atmosphere"},{"time":685000,"text":"and character with loud voices and large bodies and such,"},{"time":688000,"text":"and we had to get up and leave;"},{"time":690000,"text":"it was just that uncomfortable."},{"time":692000,"text":"And at that moment, the sun came out,"},{"time":694000,"text":"and through this perforated screen,"},{"time":697000,"text":"a pattern was cast over these bodies"},{"time":699000,"text":"and they kind of faded into the rear,"},{"time":702000,"text":"and we left the restaurant kind of"},{"time":704000,"text":"feeling O.K. about stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706000,"text":"And I do think pattern"},{"time":708000,"text":"has the capability of eradicating"},{"time":710000,"text":"some of the most evil"},{"time":712000,"text":"forces of society,"},{"time":714000,"text":"such as bad form in restaurants,"},{"time":716000,"text":"but quite seriously, it was a statement to me"},{"time":719000,"text":"that one thing that you do, sort of, see"},{"time":721000,"text":"is the aggressive nature"},{"time":723000,"text":"of the industrial world has produced --"},{"time":725000,"text":"kind of,"},{"time":728000,"text":"large masses of things,"},{"time":732000,"text":"and when you -- in monoculture,"},{"time":734000,"text":"and I think the preservation of diversity in culture"},{"time":736000,"text":"is something that's important to us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":738000,"text":"The last shots that I have deal with --"},{"time":741000,"text":"coming back to this theme of sidewalks,"},{"time":743000,"text":"and I wanted to"},{"time":745000,"text":"say something here about -- I'm, kind of, optimistic, you know."},{"time":748000,"text":"Post-Second World War,"},{"time":750000,"text":"the influence of the automobile"},{"time":752000,"text":"has really been devastating in a lot of our cities."},{"time":754000,"text":"A lot of urban areas have been converted into parking lots"},{"time":757000,"text":"in a sort of indiscriminate use."},{"time":759000,"text":"A lot of the planning departments became subordinated"},{"time":761000,"text":"to the transportation department. It's as easy to rag on cars"},{"time":763000,"text":"as it is on Wal-Mart;"},{"time":765000,"text":"I'm not going to do that."},{"time":767000,"text":"But they're real examples in urbanization"},{"time":770000,"text":"and the change that's occurred in the last number of years,"},{"time":773000,"text":"and the heightened sensitivity to the importance"},{"time":775000,"text":"of our urban environments as cultural centers."},{"time":777000,"text":"I think that they are, that the statements that we make"},{"time":780000,"text":"in this public sector"},{"time":782000,"text":"are our contributions"},{"time":785000,"text":"to a larger whole."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"Cities are the place where we're most likely"},{"time":789000,"text":"to encounter diversity"},{"time":791000,"text":"and to mix with other people."},{"time":793000,"text":"We go there for stimulation in art and all those other things."},{"time":795000,"text":"But I think people have recognized"},{"time":797000,"text":"the sanctity of our urban areas."},{"time":799000,"text":"A place like Chicago"},{"time":801000,"text":"has really reached kind of a level of international stature."},{"time":803000,"text":"The U.S. is actually becoming a bit of a leader in kind of"},{"time":805000,"text":"enlightened urban planning and renewal,"},{"time":808000,"text":"and I want to single out a place like Chicago,"},{"time":810000,"text":"where I look at some guy like Mayor Daley as a bit of a design hero"},{"time":813000,"text":"for being able to work through the"},{"time":815000,"text":"political processes and all that to improve an area."},{"time":818000,"text":"You would expect a city like this to have"},{"time":820000,"text":"upgraded flower boxes"},{"time":822000,"text":"on Michigan Avenue where wealthy people shop,"},{"time":824000,"text":"but if you actually go along the street you find"},{"time":826000,"text":"the flower boxes change from street to street:"},{"time":829000,"text":"there's actual diversity in the plants."},{"time":831000,"text":"And the idea that a city group can maintain"},{"time":833000,"text":"different types of foliage"},{"time":835000,"text":"is really quite exceptional."}]},{"cues":[{"time":838000,"text":"There are common elements of this that you'll see throughout Chicago,"},{"time":841000,"text":"and then there are your big-D design statements:"},{"time":843000,"text":"the Pritzker Pavilion done by Frank Gehry."},{"time":846000,"text":"My measure of this as being an important bit of design"},{"time":849000,"text":"is not so much the way that it looks,"},{"time":852000,"text":"but the fact that it performs a very important social function."},{"time":854000,"text":"There are a lot of free concerts, for example,"},{"time":856000,"text":"that go on in this area;"},{"time":858000,"text":"it has a phenomenal acoustic system."},{"time":860000,"text":"But the commitment that the city has made to the public area"},{"time":862000,"text":"is significant, and almost an international model."},{"time":865000,"text":"I work on the mayor's council in San Francisco,"},{"time":867000,"text":"on the International Design Council for Mayors,"},{"time":870000,"text":"and Chicago is looked at as the pinnacle,"},{"time":872000,"text":"and I really would like to salute Mayor Daley and the folks there."},{"time":875000,"text":"I thought that I should include at least one"},{"time":877000,"text":"shot of technology for you guys."},{"time":879000,"text":"This is also in Millennium Park in Chicago,"},{"time":882000,"text":"where the Spanish artist-designer Plensa"},{"time":884000,"text":"has created, kind of,"},{"time":886000,"text":"a digital readout in this park"},{"time":888000,"text":"that reflects back"},{"time":890000,"text":"the characters and personalities"},{"time":892000,"text":"of the people in this area."},{"time":895000,"text":"And it's a welcoming area, I think, inclusive of diversity,"},{"time":898000,"text":"reflective of diversity, and I think"},{"time":901000,"text":"this marriage of both technology and art"},{"time":904000,"text":"in the public sector is an area where the U.S."},{"time":906000,"text":"can really take a leadership role,"},{"time":908000,"text":"and Chicago is one example."}]},{"cues":[{"time":910000,"text":"Thank you very much."}]}]}